Class AeBPWSDefMessagePartsMapVisitor

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.AeAbstractDefVisitor
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.AeAbstractDefMessagePartsMapVisitor
          org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.AeBPWSDefMessagePartsMapVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeDefMessagePartsMapVisitor, IAeDefVisitor
public class AeBPWSDefMessagePartsMapVisitor
extends AeAbstractDefMessagePartsMapVisitor

Visits each of the wsio activities and inlines the message part information. This version differs from the WS-BPEL implementation in that it needs to account for the operation overloading. Operation overloading was supported as part of BPEL4WS but was disallowed by WS-i Basic Profile and removed from the WS-BPEL specification.
